## Copy and Move Objects

```typescript
// Rename a file (move to new path within same bucket)
const { data, error } = await supabase.storage
  .from('uploads')
  .move('user-id/temp-upload.jpg', 'user-id/profile-avatar.jpg')

// Copy a file to a different path
const { data, error } = await supabase.storage
  .from('uploads')
  .copy('templates/invoice-template.pdf', `${user.id}/my-invoice.pdf`)

// Move to a different bucket
const { data, error } = await supabase.storage
  .from('uploads')
  .move('user-id/file.jpg', 'archive/user-id/file.jpg', {
    destinationBucket: 'archive-bucket'
  })
```

