## Egress Optimisation Tips

```typescript
// Use image transformations to reduce bandwidth
// Serve 100x100 thumbnail instead of 4000x4000 original
const { data } = supabase.storage.from('uploads').getPublicUrl(filePath, {
  transform: {
    width: 200,
    height: 200,
    resize: 'cover',
    quality: 80,
    format: 'webp',    // webp is 25-35% smaller than jpeg for same quality
  }
})

// Use <Image> component for automatic format/size optimisation
// next.config.ts must include the Supabase storage domain in remotePatterns
import Image from 'next/image'
<Image
  src={avatarUrl}
  width={100} height={100}
  alt="Avatar"
  // Next.js automatically serves correct size for device pixel ratio
/>
```
